1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about tokenization BPE than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:09,600
Tokenization BPE, or Byte Pair Encoding, reduces text into smaller, manageable pieces.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:11,600
But why does this matter?

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:14,400
It enhances language models' understanding of context.

5
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:20,000
Studies show models using BPE perform better with less data, but results can vary.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,800
Understanding tokenization BPE is key to grasping AI advancements in language processing.

